      "value": "<div title=\"Page 57\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>Upon casting this spell, you turn invisible, as @Compendium[sfrpg.spells.YDXegEus8p0BnsH1]{Invisibility}, and you choose a second target. That creature can still see you as though you weren&rsquo;t invisible, and you can attack that creature without ending the invisibility effffect. If you attack any other creature, this spell ends. If you cast this spell multiple times, you can attack any of the affffected creatures without ending the spell.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
